<div style='font-size: 12px;'><p>This tab displays the lists to which the current user has access using the permissions for the clickstat/mviews page. These permissions control whether the current user may see all lists, only those lists of which he is the owner, or does not have access to the plugin.</p><table><tr><td>Name</td><td>The list name. This is a link to the Messages tab, which will display the messages sent to the list.<p>When there is more than one list, then an extra row, 'All lists', is displayed. This is a link to the messages tab that will display all sent messages.<p>If a list has not had any messages sent to it, then the list name will not be a link.</td></tr><tr><td >Active</td><td>Whether the list is active.</td></tr><tr><td >Total sent</td><td>The number of messages that have been sent to the list.</td></tr><tr><td >Latest</td><td>The most recent message that has been sent to the list. This is a link to the Opened tab, which will display the users who belong to the list and have opened the message.</td></tr></table></div>